## Architecture / Arquitectura

Basic layout:

mistral/agents/agents_api/financial_analyst/
├── mcp_servers_by_latinett-&-arm-block-chain-financial-enterprise-global-group/
│   ├── stdio_yfinance_server.py          # Data retrieval from Yahoo Finance
│   ├── stdio_report_gen_server.py        # LLM (MistralIH) report generation server
│   └── stdio_save_report_server.py       # Persist reports to disk
├── async_run_report_gen_mcp.py          # Example orchestrator to run servers and tasks
└── README.md.goet.arm-latínett           # This file

Simple description:
- stdio_yfinance_server.py: obtains quotes, historical prices and fundamentals.
- stdio_report_gen_server.py: calls MistralIH (agents API) to generate analysis text and structured recommendations.
- stdio_save_report_server.py: saves outputs to files (md, json, optionally PDF via converters).

