## Installation / Instalación

Prerequisites:
- Python 3.10+ (recommended)
- Virtualenv / venv
- Internet access to call data providers and MistralIH API

Example setup:

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

(If no requirements.txt exists, add the dependencies used by your servers: requests, yfinance, mistral-client (or equivalent), fastapi/uvicorn for MCP endpoints, etc.)

Requisitos:
- Python 3.10+
- Virtualenv/venv
- Acceso a Internet para proveedores de datos y a la API de MistralIH

