## Environment / Variables de entorno

Set your MistralIH API key:

```bash
export MISTRAL_API_KEY="your_api_key_here"
```

Configure any data provider keys (e.g., Yahoo, AlphaVantage) as environment variables expected by the servers.

Configure las claves necesarias para proveedores de datos y la API de MistralIH como variables de entorno.

---

## Usage / Uso

Run data and report servers (examples):

```bash
# Start the MCP servers (example names)
python mcp_servers_by_latinett-&-arm-block-chain-financial-enterprise-global-group/stdio_yfinance_server.py
python mcp_servers_by_latinett-&-arm-block-chain-financial-enterprise-global-group/stdio_report_gen_server.py
python mcp_servers_by_latinett-&-arm-block-chain-financial-enterprise-global-group/stdio_save_report_server.py

# Run the orchestrator to generate a report
python async_run_report_gen_mcp.py --symbol AAPL --output reports/aapl_report.md
```

Then open the generated markdown file or query the running agent via its API (if exposed).

